<h3>Media queries breakpoint</h3>
<ul class="list-unstyled">
    <li><code>respond-to($media)</code></li>
    <li><code>respond-to-free($target-1, $media-1, $target-2: null, $media-2: null)</code></li>
</ul>
<p>One of the most important mixin responsible for media queries and breakpoints for the purpose of RWD.<br>
    Available media breakpoints: <code>$mobile</code>, <code>$phone</code>, <code>$tablet</code>, <code>$tablet--xs</code>, <code>$desktop</code>, <code>$desktop--xl</code> <br>
</p>
<p><code>$mobile</code> is responsible for range phone + tablet.</p>
<p>Breakpoints are defined in <a class="link-neutral" href="https://github.com/r4fx/mate/blob/master/src/styles/scss/_settings.scss" target="_blank">main settings file</a></p>

<p>Examples:</p>

<div class="code-example">
    <div data-clone class="hidden">
        body {
            font-size: 3rem;

            @include respond-to($mobile) {
                font-size: 1.6rem;
            }

            @include respond-to-free(min-width, 750px, max-width, 850px) {
                bottom: 25%;
            }
        }
    </div>
    <pre lang="scss"></pre>
</div>

